voluntary self-sacrifice.

00:44:38.349 --> 00:44:41.719
This is the matter:
this is the image that Milton

00:44:41.719 --> 00:44:45.300
had established in his defenses
of his blindness.

00:44:45.300 --> 00:44:47.883
Milton had written in the
sonnet that we looked at on

00:44:47.883 --> 00:44:49.324
Monday to Mr.
Cyriack Skinner,

00:44:49.324 --> 00:44:52.405
and he had also written in the
Second Defense of the English

00:44:52.405 --> 00:44:54.556
