00:44:54.556 --> 00:44:58.289
sacrificed his sight for the
good of his fellow Englishmen.

00:44:58.289 --> 00:45:02.677
He lost his eyes "overplied in
liberty's defence,

00:45:02.677 --> 00:45:07.429
my noble task," Milton had
written in that sonnet.

00:45:07.429 --> 00:45:09.795
In the Second
