write his regicide treatises

00:45:13.005 --> 00:45:15.990
despite the advice of his
doctors who insisted that he

00:45:15.990 --> 00:45:19.200
would go blind if he continued
-- that's how important the

00:45:19.200 --> 00:45:21.960
project was for Milton and the
sacrifice.

00:45:21.960 --> 00:45:25.336
You begin to see a way in which
the two dominant features of

00:45:25.336 --> 00:45:28.828
Book Three, Milton's invocation
to light and the discussion of

00:45:28.828 --> 00:45:32.719
blindness therein and the dialog
between the Father and the Son,

00:45:32.719 --> 00:45:37.386
are speaking to one another and
they're functioning in a kind of

00:45:37.386 --> 00:45:41.979
parallel fashion.Just as the
