of Paradise Lost is

00:45:48.727 --> 00:45:51.469
essentially an inheritance
narrative.

00:45:51.469 --> 00:45:55.286
The Son's voluntary sacrifice
will be rewarded with his

00:45:55.286 --> 00:45:57.829
inheritance of all of God's
power.

00:45:57.829 --> 00:46:01.143
Presumably too,
Milton's sacrifice will also be

00:46:01.143 --> 00:46:05.685
rewarded by God.
It's as if Milton wants the

00:46:05.685 --> 00:46:12.415
